caption:
Weight loss is 80 to 90% about eating properly and maintaining a healthy diet! üíØüôåüèª

10 - 20% depends on exercise! I did not lose weight overnight, I have been strictly following this routine for more than 1 and half years now! üòäüí™üèª

I stopped having sugar! I did not have any form of sugar for 4 months! Literally, zero sugar and that was the only reason that I saw some weight dropping! üö´‚ö†Ô∏è

I am on intermittent fasting. I only eat two meals a day between 12 pm to 8 pm! The other time I can't eat solids but consumed liquids! 

I drink green tea two times a day. Although, I did not exercise or go to the gym! I am extremely active and I make sure that I complete 10,000 steps every day. You can start with 5,000 steps and work your way up!

I am not a professional, I did not consult anyone! This may not be recommended by a professional and I do not ask anyone to try this because what works for me may not work for you! Everyone's body is different. Fortunately, the above method worked for me! I still only have something sweet once a week! 

I have lost 30kgs+ so far, however, I have a long way to go and would like to lose more and get more in shape! üëäüèªüôà

It wasn‚Äôt easy but it was absolutely worth it! üôèüèª I know the struggle, I was fat all my life and I am the biggest foodie I have ever known and if I could do it, trust me anyone can! ‚ù§Ô∏èüòÅ
